item.title: Join
item.description: Chi Epsilon at UCLA Join Us Chi Epsilon seeks to foster excellence, connectivity and engagement among those in the civil engineering community to improve our world, and we are always happy to help qualified members become a part of this society. National Chi Epsilon Why Join? Your achievement in scholastic endeavors is recognized and appreciated. Chi Epsilon is no obscure honors society; it is the National Civil Engineering Honor Society.

item.title: Officers
item.description: Officers Camryn Lopez President Camryn Lopez is a senior civil engineering major interested in pursuing a career in hydrology. She currently works as an intern for a civil engineering company learning about the design of civil infrastructure. Camryn is also passionate about supporting and encouraging women in STEM through the Society of Women Engineers (SWE) and outreach. Outside of the classroom, she enjoys dancing, tennis, and crocheting.
